# @desc   Tap Submit/Confirm on the IOU confirmation page. Triggers ManualCreateExpenseSubmit, ManualSubmitToDestinationVisible, and ManualCreateExpenseServerResponse. If the device has location permission granted, ManualGeolocationWait fires as a child of Submit. Requires being on the confirmation page already (chain after a Create Expense flow).
# @pre    role="button" label="Confirm"
# @post   role="button" label="Open actions menu"
# @tag    iou
# @tag    perf
# @tag    sentry-ManualCreateExpenseSubmit
# @tag    sentry-ManualSubmitToDestinationVisible
# @tag    sentry-ManualCreateExpenseServerResponse
# @tag    sentry-ManualGeolocationWait
press "role=\"button\" label=\"Confirm\" || role=\"button\" label=\"Submit\" || label=\"Confirm\" || label=\"Submit\""
